# AutoResearch Kit — Events Log
# Format: [YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM:SS] [exp#NNN] EVENT_TYPE: description
#
# Event types:
#   SESSION_START  — new research session begins
#   BASELINE       — baseline metric established
#   PHASE_GATE     — phase transition triggered (sequential experiments only)
#   METRIC_SWITCH  — primary metric changed
#   INSIGHT        — significant finding worth highlighting
#   SESSION_END    — session complete with summary
